OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FThe family of a law student who
OL,7,Fdisappeared in Bristol exactly two
OL,8,Fyears ago say they are still desperate
OL,9,Ffor answers about what happened to him.
OL,11,FJack O'Sullivan was 22 years old when
OL,12,Fhe went missing after leaving a house
OL,13,Fparty in the Hotwells area of the city
OL,14,Fon 2 March 2024.
OL,16,FHe was last seen on CCTV walking along
OL,17,FBrunel Lock Road at just after 3am.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
