OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FDespite numerous searches by the
OL,7,Fcommunity and police - including
OL,8,Funderwater river searches from
OL,9,FAvonmouth to Conham River Park - there
OL,10,Fhas been no sign of Jack in the past
OL,11,Ftwo years.
OL,13,FHis disappearance has captured the
OL,14,Fattention of more than 100,000 people
OL,15,Fwho have joined the 'FIND JACK'
OL,16,FFacebook page, which posts regular
OL,17,Fappeals for information.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
