OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said they
OL,7,Fhave reviewed more than 100 hours'
OL,8,Fworth of CCTV footage in their
OL,9,Finvestigation into Jack's
OL,10,Fdisappearance and searched in water
OL,11,Fand on land using a mounted team, dog
OL,12,Funit and drone unit in the Hotwells,
OL,13,FAshton and North Somerset areas.
OL,15,FBut in June 2024, three months after
OL,16,Fhis disappearance, his family made a
OL,17,Fformal complaint to Avon and Somerset
OL,18,FPolice about their handling of the
OL,19,Fcase.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
