OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772618688
OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FAn investigation of the force's
OL,7,Fhandling of the case was carried out
OL,8,Fafter the complaints and a report was
OL,9,Fwritten.
OL,11,FThat report concluded that officers
OL,12,Fhad conducted an "in-depth, exhaustive
OL,13,Finvestigation into the disappearance
OL,14,Fof Jack."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
