OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FInvestigators did however note that
OL,7,FJack's case was not placed on the
OL,8,FMissing People charity's database at
OL,9,Fthe 'earliest reasonable opportunity',
OL,10,Fwhich, provides Avon and Somerset
OL,11,FPolice says provides them with a
OL,12,F"learning" for the future.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
