OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FReflecting on the two year
OL,7,Fanniversary, Avon and Somerset
OL,8,FPolice's Assistant Chief Constable
OL,9,FJoanne Hall said: "As we reach the
OL,10,Fsecond anniversary of Jack O'Sullivan
OL,11,Fgoing missing, I wholeheartedly
OL,12,Frecognise the devastating impact his
OL,13,Fdisappearance continues to have on his
OL,14,Floved ones.
OL,16,F"We know how difficult it is for
OL,17,FJack's family that, despite extensive
OL,18,Fenquiries, we have not yet been able
OL,19,Fto find him or provide the conclusive
OL,20,Fanswers they so desperately need.
OL,26,@qD@SOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
