OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FFrom the outset we've always had a
OL,7,Fshared aim of finding Jack and this
OL,8,Fintention has been at the heart of
OL,9,Fevery action we've taken and decisions
OL,10,Fwe've made.
OL,12,F"Alongside our ongoing investigation,
OL,13,Fwe have also drawn on specialist
OL,14,Fexpertise and independent agencies to
OL,15,Freview, test and assure our work,
OL,16,Fensuring that any further
OL,17,Fopportunities for enquiry are fully
OL,18,Fexplored. At every stage we have been
OL,19,Fled by the evidence and pursued the
OL,20,Frelevant lines of enquiry.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
