OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,F"It's important to stress that this
OL,7,Fremains a live investigation. If
OL,8,Fanyone has information that could
OL,9,Fassist our enquiries, please contact
OL,10,Fus online through our website, or call
OL,11,F101, quoting reference number
OL,12,F5224055172."
OL,14,FThis evening, Mrs O'Sullivan's church
OL,15,Fcommunity will mark the day.
OL,17,F"We are going to say prayers and light
OL,18,Fa candle in the hope that that light
OL,19,Fwill be able to guide Jack home," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
