OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FHis last confirmed sighting was on
OL,7,FCCTV at 3:13am in which he is seen
OL,8,Fwalking across a grassy area at the
OL,9,Fjunction of Brunel Lock Way and Brunel
OL,10,FWay.
OL,12,FAt 3:24am, Jack attempted to call a
OL,13,Ffriend who was at the party. Jack
OL,14,Fanswered when the friend called back,
OL,15,Fbut the line went dead.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
