OL,3,CTwo years on: What do we know about
OL,4,Cmissing student Jack O'Sullivan?
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police said there
OL,7,Fwere two further potential CCTV
OL,8,Fsightings of Jack: crossing the
OL,9,FPlimsol Bridge back towards the city
OL,10,Fcentre at 3:25am and walking on the
OL,11,FBennett Way slip road at 3:38am.
OL,13,FHis phone remained active on the Find
OL,14,FMy Friends app until 6:44am.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
